            <h1>
              <strong>Staff Logistics</strong>
            </h1>
            <p class="summary">Staffing the oil and gas industry…</p>
            <p>With a unique approach.</p>
            <p>A valuable and highly specialised service, which keeps expatriate workforces optimally deployed.</p>
            <p>Staff Logistics offer a complete employment package for companies operating in Algeria. Services include recruitment, visa and work permit processing, travel and accommodation arrangements, pay-rolling preparation, comprehensive insurance and medevac provision, payment of local taxes and social security contributions.</p>
            <p>The Company has established a unique method of operation, whereby staff can be moved freely from one project to another on Staff Logistics’ work permits. This has tremendous benefits for those organisations with multiple operations in country.</p>
            <p>Its knowledgeable team of British and Algerian personnel offer professional advice, speedy responses and all round first class support.</p>
            <br>
